shes.json, menuTiming.json, quirkCases.json, saveLoad.json, scriptedMechanics.json), 31 fixtures under test/oracles/fixtures/ (the capture-*.json fixtures inventoried in step 01-015), and one manifest under reference/manifests/ (c1-complete.json), without embedding proprietary id Software bytes from the bundled DOOM.EXE, DOOMD.EXE, DOOM1.WAD, or DEFAULT.CFG references that some tests cross-check against via reference/policy.ts REFERENCE_BUNDLE_PATH at run time.",
